{"tid":9761,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"窮學生鏡頭求指點","createTime":"2016-11-28T16:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T13:35:19.000Z","uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ad36794eef2a74549faff3ddfed7ec9419a648","tid":9761,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟係個窮學生 有支canon18-55kit 自己好憎啲塊鏡 冇乜用過<br />\n另外平時用開canon 50f1.8 影景同特殊情況就用sigma10-20mm<br />\n問題就黎喇 小弟影學校活動啲相 特別係頒獎典禮啲相個陣 50mm影唔哂 10-20又太wide同唔太夠sharp<br />\n想問各位巴打有冇推薦咩平既變焦鏡&lt;5000<br />\nRange我諗就唔洗太闊 岩用就得 最緊要夠型同sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然定焦夠sharp 不過都想變焦 方便做野<br />\n非ff"},{"pid":"22aa4c291d1b54f4cb289123b26b6ffd2e92fb3a","tid":9761,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  學校野用kit 冇投訴啦"},{"pid":"8a21c9120ebaae5fc696215725602d8a05a85050","tid":9761,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"用kit加flash夠做啦"},{"pid":"8935706c2736f480ead072012fcc75d4a22bb9f8","tid":9761,"uid":32279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"點樣夠型法<br />\n要型直接買紅圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEfs17-50 f/2.8 <br />\n如果暫時唔上ff <br />\n呢支夠晒你影<br />\n夠sharp又常用焦距"},{"pid":"737d617c9d3038b318d01da415eb51a7b61e3413","tid":9761,"uid":36511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"Sigma 18-35 art <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c10263cd44b87f25d95c4b8adc8ccc3062f2b9c","tid":9761,"uid":36658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"1855加個hood即刻pro晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSigma 1750啦一定夠做"},{"pid":"46c0dd6fef9b469c85243d989ff59a8911698251","tid":9761,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1855加個hood即刻pro晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSigma 1750啦一定夠做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁拎部大部啲既鏡點都型過kit+hood<br />\n1750真心諗過 但水貨係咪易走焦？<br />\n有冇其他差唔多價錢可以比較下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcb09b78ea029be393c68f61423f52ff91b26ac","tid":9761,"uid":19933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"平玩就sigma 1770"},{"pid":"dd6059a415f66a2dfe57499ba627f140ca641cb8","tid":9761,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sigma 18-35 art <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似又型又sharp 但好似好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0911685253fe088339f0148d572057b52b7d30","tid":9761,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:02:48.000Z","msg":"其實你都識講你係輸學生...支kit除左唔靚仔之外有咩問題?<br />\n<br />\n你有錢不如買下accessory啦"},{"pid":"4d194687c6b830562ed6007350b76411c4d5ac48","tid":9761,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"用閃光燈打bounding +PS 後制，已經夠玩喎Ching"},{"pid":"1f7f314051529ce994fff1fdfd11b761e9bb02c3","tid":9761,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"裝直倒"},{"pid":"b61240df91c6b14f42820807162cd37f07476ae6","tid":9761,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你都識講你係輸學生...支kit除左唔靚仔之外有咩問題?<br />\n<br />\n你有錢不如買下accessory啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打既建議 但係基本野都有齊 而且小弟鏡頭佔有慾好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10958b6cf41466a64b688602a40161fd3e16991","tid":9761,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"